msgctxt "84_Inconsiderate Date"
msgid "What're you doing?"
msgstr "¿Qué haces?"

msgctxt "96_Girl Glued to a Screen"
msgid "Hm? Playing pachinko."
msgstr "¿Mm? Jugando pachinko."

msgctxt "108_Inconsiderate Date"
msgid "Pachinko? On your phone?"
msgstr "¿Pachinko? ¿En el celular?"

msgctxt "120_Girl Glued to a Screen"
msgid "Yeah. It's called 777 Town. You haven't heard of it? It's an app that lets you play pachinko or slots on your phone or anywhere."
msgstr "Sí. En 777 Town. ¿No la conoces? Es una app que te permite jugar pachinko o tragamonedas en tu celu o donde sea."

msgctxt "132_Inconsiderate Date"
msgid "Wow, that's cool! Let me try!"
msgstr "¡Guau, qué genial! ¡A ver, déjame probarlo!"

msgctxt "144_Girl Glued to a Screen"
msgid "No way. Don't you have a date soon? And by soon, I mean like, now?"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¿No tienes una cita pronto? Y por pronto, me refiero a, ¡ahora mismo!"

msgctxt "156_Inconsiderate Date"
msgid "Oh, come on! Just one game, then I'll go!"
msgstr "¡Oh, vamos! ¡Una partidita y me voy!"

msgctxt "168_Player"
msgid "(777 Town? Sounds like something the girls at the club might be into.)"
msgstr "(¿777 Town? Suena a algo que les podría gustar a las chicas del club)."

